{"type": "article", "id": 12442, "title": "皮革制花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-22T07:45:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115235RcvptymU4ed6axkN.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tROEX 设计工作室推出的这一套花瓶是一次皮革制作实验的结果，整套花瓶全部使用皮革制成，形状的设计灵感来自植物内部的隔膜管道，基底所用的橡胶膜大小决定花瓶的尺寸，有小型、中型和大型三种尺寸选择，外部的接缝保证结构上的完整，看上去很是别致。<a href=\"http://studioroex.com/product_detail/plumbers-piece.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140155mBNh6gyK91VJkWDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140155pFLlD4SuMbAxCTfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614015584vE3AuSK1qsrwfc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140156AfdxthPDTmyZXYL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}